name: UTDEasyParking
0:
”Alexa, open Parking Assist.”
”I have Orange Parking.”
”I am a Visitor”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: parking assist
des:
Ever have trouble finding parking at UTD? Late to that important class or meeting because you couldn't find that spot? Well this is the tool for you!

Our Alexa Skill provides you with the ability to locate open parking spaces at specific locations at the ease of a voice command. Have limited green parking? No problem! With the help of this Alexa app, you will have no trouble finding a spot for yourself when you're on the rush. Orange? Enjoy your luxurious experience of choosing equal to lower tier spots that are closest to your class!

Try UTD Easy Parking today!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
